{"priority": "blocker", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398/building-editor-its-not-possible-to-select"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1398/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "title": "Building Editor: It's not possible to select draw modes", "component": {"name": "gui::BuildingEditor", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122887.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 1, "content": {"raw": "1. Open Building Editor\r\n\r\n2. On the palette, click on any brush\r\n\r\n3. The brush becomes selected but nothing else works. It's not possible to draw on the 2D View.\r\n\r\nThis happens because the draw mode is cancelled immediately after, from `EditorView::OnColorSelected`.\r\n\r\nNot sure why, but this is only happening after the latest commits.\r\n\r\nI have a solution [here](#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/034ca8fe1995f72ca339bcf3e2498eb8e9a276f8)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open Building Editor</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>On the palette, click on any brush</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The brush becomes selected but nothing else works. It's not possible to draw on the 2D View.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>This happens because the draw mode is cancelled immediately after, from <code>EditorView::OnColorSelected</code>.</p>\n<p>Not sure why, but this is only happening after the latest commits.</p>\n<p>I have a solution <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/034ca8fe1995f72ca339bcf3e2498eb8e9a276f8\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-12-22T15:57:41.406419+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:45:06.766214+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1398}